GET /goals list all goals for a specific user. 
GET /goals/{GoalId} fetchign specific goal 

Edit page: /goals/{GoalId}/edit

PUT /goals/{GoalId}/update 





Login: 
token headers, ?token=




goals/{userid}/{GoalId}




URL
/goals will show you the list of goals. 
/goals/create will show you the form to create a new goal. 
/goals/{id} show page. 
/goals/{id}/edit edit page. 


API, backend 
GET /goals this will return all goals 
GET /goals/{id}
POST /goals create a new goal. 
PUT /goals/{id}/update updated a specific goal 
DELETE /goals/{id}


RESTful 
/goals/{id}
